## Summary
This documentation explains Amplitude's Compass Chart, a tool designed to identify user behaviors that predict retention by analyzing correlations between initial actions and long-term engagement. It provides step-by-step instructions for creating a Compass Chart, including selecting cohorts, events, properties, and setting time periods for analysis.

